        <abstract> 
<p>Did not get appointment to poultry department of the <hi rend="italic">Field</hi>; W. B. Tegetmeier has the position.</p> 
            <p>His lawsuit concluded well but expensive. Thanks CD for aid during his distress; encloses cheque.</p>
